parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or become stuck in gear, leading to accidents, injuries, or strandings.
symptoms: The transmission exhibits difficulty shifting in lower gears
the vehicle loses power
the transmission slips or hesitates
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear
the transmission locks up
the vehicle goes into "limp" mode
the transmission fluid pressure sensor malfunctions
the vehicle moves in reverse when the gear selector is in "drive" and vice versa.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission converter can cause the transmission to malfunction, leading to accidents, injuries, or strandings.
symptoms: The transmission converter fails
the RPM needle goes up and down on stealth mode
the wiper hose keeps coming off
the back-up camera keeps going black
the AC goes out
the software will not update
the eco system will not work properly
the passenger bag is not detected.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission fluid pressure sensor can cause the transmission to malfunction, leading to accidents, injuries, or strandings.
symptoms: The transmission fluid pressure sensor malfunctions
the vehicle goes into "limp" mode
the transmission slips or hesitates
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ABS hydraulic control unit can cause the brakes to suddenly engage, leading to sudden deceleration, wheel lock-up, and loss of control, which can result in accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Sudden slowing or stopping of the vehicle
wheel hop
brake pedal feels soft or spongy
brakes lock up
burning smell from brakes
vehicle decelerates quickly when lifting foot off the gas pedal
steering shakes or vibrates.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbags to deploy in the event of a crash can increase the risk of injury or fatality to the occupants, especially in severe impacts.
symptoms: Airbags do not deploy despite the severity of the crash
occupants experience injuries that could have been mitigated by airbag deployment
onboard collision sensor is triggered but airbags do not deploy.
